            <div class="panel panel--info panel--simple u-mb-m">
                <div class="panel__body">
                    <p>You will no longer have access to the surveys you transfer. If you still require access to your surveys, you can <a href="/prototypes/user-account-creation/version-4/account/03-share-access-to-my-surveys/index.html">share access</a>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2 class="u-fs-m">What happens?</h2>
